      "acceptanceCriteria": "Material properties (Ti-6Al-4V: E=114 GPa, sigma_y=880 MPa) sourced from ASTM F136 and supplier certificates. Geometry from certified CMM measurements of test articles. Friction coefficient from published Ti-Ti contact literature (range 0.15–0.25).",
      "rationale": "All model inputs traceable to primary sources. Titanium alloy elastic modulus and friction coefficient identified in screening as dominant QoI drivers; nominal values used with bounds documented. Geometry inputs verified against CMM reports for each of the 11 test constructs. Gradation 3 achieved."
