      "rationale": "Eleven constructs from two independent laboratories (Lab 1: n=6, Lab 2: n=5) sourced from the same production lot. CMM dimensional inspection certificates available. Inter-laboratory coefficient of variation for stiffness < 4.2%, confirming reproducible sample preparation. Gradation 3 achieved."
    },
