      "rationale": "ASTM F1717 protocol followed at both laboratories with documented load rate (5 mm/min), ambient temperature, and fixture alignment procedures. However, only a single test configuration (compression-bending, no torsion or tension-bending) was evaluated. This limits condition coverage relative to the full COU envelope. Gradation 2 achieved against required Gradation 3; gap acknowledged and accepted given device risk level and availability of supplementary analytical bounds.",
